import React from 'react' import './about.css' const About = () => { return (

About

  • George is a Senior Lecturer at the University of Maryland with a Master of Arts in Communicating Arts with an emphasis in Speech Communication from the University of Wisconsin-Superior.
  • George is passionate about teaching students important skills such as public speaking and presenting to audiences. He has helped students develop their interpersonal skills and taught students how to accomplish things out of their comfort zone.
  • Outside of teaching, George is a Master Scuba Diver with multiple scuba diving certifications and is a member of Project Aware Shark Conservation.
) } export default About;
